Author: navgate2051
Text: Yes, absolutely you're not alone. That's been my struggle as of the last few months. I've lost almost 70 pounds but recently something is making me eat more than I should.    I think it's like unclogging a drain. The water continues to rise more and more but unless you do the work of actually finding the problem (that emotion) it won't go away. If you've ever unclogged a drain it's the most satisfying feeling after working on it all day.
